$Header: $


REVISION HISTORY:


0.1
	- Created module

0.2
	- Changed the name from SimpleMySQL to DBD::mysql::SimpleMySQL
	- Added perldoc documentation and added additional values that can be passed to dbconnect

0.3
	- Fixed "package" line to match new name

0.4
	- "Overloaded" build_select function to all you to pass either 5 args (select, from, joins, wheres, order)
          or 1 arg (hashref containing select, from, joins, wheres, order keys)
	- Fixed bug in "build_select" that returned a blank WHERE statement when an empty arrayref was passed in
          causing a broken select statement to be created.

0.5	
	- Fixed stupid syntax error :)
